This folder contains files related with Landsat 8 image processing.

PyQGIS scripts for graphical modeler to process Landsat 8 images:
* Landsat8ReadBandParameters.py - scripts reads Landsat 8 metafile and returns N band parameters;
* Landsat8ReadImageParameters.py - scripts reads Landsat 8 metafile and returns common parameters: {sun elevation, sun distance};
* DNToToaReflectance.py - script converts DN values of Landsat 8 image to Toa Reflectance with sun elevation correction;
* NDVI.py - script calculates NDVI.

